+  not configured, say so plainly rather than claiming to have sent something.
+
   When sending communications:
   - Be professional and clear
   - Include relevant context
   - Follow up appropriately
+  - After a successful send related to a lead, update that lead's status/notes via crm_leads
   
   When scheduling:
   - Check availability
